        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>I tend to pay attention to John's comments because I value his perspective and feel that he had valuable insights to offer. However, I believe that his approach may not be suitable for companies that are not yet prepared to embrace the RCM2 methodology.

